Name:           python3-schedutils
Summary:        Linux scheduler python bindings
Version:        0.6
Release:        1%{?dist}
Group:          Development/Languages/Python
Vendor:         VMware, Inc.
Distribution:   Photon
License:        GPLv2
URL:            https://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/libs/python/python-schedutils/python-schedutils.git/
